<indexterm><primary>D_byte</primary><secondary>D_byte</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>D_byte</primary><secondary>D_byte</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>D_byte::D_byte (MbedI2C * ptr, int addr)</computeroutput></para>
<para>Create a new byte for this i/o expander The hardware i/o expander provides four input and four output bits. </para>
</section>
